  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Antares is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>A hot and cold buffet breakfast is served every morning with lots of options to set you up for the day. </p>
<p>In the evening, indulge in a four-course meal with choices including an antipasto and salad buffet. There's a candlelit Tyrolean gala dinner every week, which is a great chance to try some local dishes.</p>
<p>Every afternoon between 3pm and 5pm, tuck into the free afternoon buffet where you'll be treated to goodies like soup, cold meats and cakes.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year's Eve gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
