  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Antares has a great location in <a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> with the Ciampinoi lift being a stones throw away. After a day of exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites Ski Area</a> head back to the hotel and enjoy relaxing in the wellness area with an indoor pool. </p>
<h2>Cosy Atmosphere </h2>
<p>The spacious, comfortable rooms have a traditional alpine feel to them with warm wood and soft furnishings throughout. With rooms sleeping up to three people, this cosy hotel is a great option for families looking for central accommodation in Selva. </p>
<p>Each day you can fuel up for a day on the mountain at the breakfast buffet with sweet and savoury options available, and when you return for the day enjoy a delicious evening meal in the cosy and warm restaurant. There is often a weekly South Tyrol themed dinner, so you can sample some of the specialities from the area - whether its canederli, spätzle or apple strudel, you'll be in for a treat.</p>
<h2>Wellness</h2>
<p>When you return from a day of skiing, make the most of the swimming pool and wellness area. Have a dip in the pool, unwind in the saunas or revitalise in the chromotherapy showers- and for a little extra, book to use the outdoor jacuzzi with views of the resort. Pamper yourself and book in for a beauty treatment or massage with the in-house experts (pay locally). And for those who want to stay active, even off of the slopes, there is a fitness room with a range of equipment available for you to use. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Antares the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
